title: Assignment 2
description: This assignment is an exploratory data analysis on data from various households in Massachusetts, with the goal to learn about the effects of zoning.

title: Assignment 3
description: This assignment is an analysis and revision of a graph displaying data on COVID-19 cases from 2020 to 2022.

title: Assignment 4
image: images/Race Distribution of Complaints against NYC Police Officers.png
description: This assignment is a demonstration of how different design choices for a visualization can change a viewer's perception of the given data, using NYPD complaint data as an example.
